Megatron looks back from the screen, this was more important. "Very well
Autofire. Go down to the infermery, I'll be right there." He then walks
away from Autofire, and back outside. "Scourge, I need your assistance" he
barks.

Motormaster arrives at the CR chamber. He puts Wildrider in, and pushes the
activation button. He then climbs into one himself, and presses the switch,
and can slowly feel himself fall into stasis lock, as the fluid surounds
him.
